               <p>I live in Knightsbridge; on the 9th of July I was not at home at the time, I went out at seven, and returned before ten, and missed my things.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17920912-22-person240">
                  SARAH
                   HAWKES
               <interp inst="t17920912-22-person240" type="surname" value="HAWKES"></interp>
