                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I live opposite the prosecutor, my husband and he came home from work; and he has a bit of ground, and they went down to his ground, and in about a quarter after, I saw the prisoner in his room, up two pair of stairs, at the drawers; and in a quarter of an hour afterwards I saw her go out with a bundle; the woman she robbed had been very ill, and she attended her.</p>
               <p>
            
